  "detailed_description": "Bauer is a side-scrolling endless runner fun little game where you help a simple mouse fly his plane and avoid all the obstacles in the air.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779130/extras/4ebd486865e71802f7b3fd7eb8a161d9.poster.avif?t=1650295069\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779130/extras/4ebd486865e71802f7b3fd7eb8a161d9.webm?t=1650295069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779130/extras/4ebd486865e71802f7b3fd7eb8a161d9.mp4?t=1650295069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bauer's dream, ever since he was a child, was to become the first mouse to fly a plane. After working on his own plane for a long time he is finally ready to test it. But he will need your help to avoid all the traffic in the air! It is busy up there. Learn how to use the special skills, see how far you can go and try to get the highest score. Oh and have fun!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Special Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Entirely hand drawn<br></li><li> Family friendly<br></li><li> Replayable<br></li><li> Multiple Game Modes</li></ul><br>",
